2577public void testCompletionCatchArgumentName2() throws JavaScriptModelException {

2579        
2580        Object argumentPrefixPreviousValue = options.get(JavaScriptCore.CODEASSIST_ARGUMENT_PREFIXES);
2581        options.put(JavaScriptCore.CODEASSIST_ARGUMENT_PREFIXES,"arg"); //$NON-NLS-1$
2582        Object localPrefixPreviousValue = options.get(JavaScriptCore.CODEASSIST_LOCAL_PREFIXES);
2583        options.put(JavaScriptCore.CODEASSIST_LOCAL_PREFIXES,"loc"); //$NON-NLS-1$
2584        
2585        JavaScriptCore.setOptions(options);
2586        
2587        try {
2588                CompletionTestsRequestor requestor = new CompletionTestsRequestor();
2589                IJavaScriptUnit cu= getCompilationUnit("Completion", "src", "", "CompletionCatchArgumentName2.js");

2595        
2596                assertEquals(
2597                        "element:exception    completion:exception    relevance:"+(R_DEFAULT + R_INTERESTING + R_CASE + R_NON_RESTRICTED)+"\n"+

2600        } finally {
